Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's not waste time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.  Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry, I'm broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had that carpet... Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.61,0:00:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Help!  The monster within me is about to explode!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within Johan... there are two personalities!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:22.99,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,312)\fad(392)}The Fifth Spoonful of Sugar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this was what happened:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you stopped by that warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Asian man and the arsonist were already fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Asian ran away when he noticed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this correct, Miss Anna Liebert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the suspect is a man from a fascist group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's admitted his crime by talking about \N some fire for a festival for some ethnic group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we've confirmed your identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you may go for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I can go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the people in that town called the Asian "Dr. Tenma."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you happen to know anything about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by her appearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you think she was trying to \N become a prostitute in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the people from the Turkish town
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,called that Asian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, after we told them he was \N a suspect in a series of homicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we began our questioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and every single one of them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,said that they had no idea who he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I acted as your guardian this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rosso...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Anna?  I was worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just disappeared all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You changed clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stuff you were wearing didn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rosso, aren't you having anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you still put five spoonfuls of sugar in your coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee is no good if it's not sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked so depressed, even \N though you're here for a job interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it so funny that I put so much sugar in my coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Anna...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are hired!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With such a pretty girl working here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my restaurant will get plenty of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,smile a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your pretty face go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so gung-ho about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this is an Italian restaurant \N in the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being "busy" here doesn't mean much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go around that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put the food out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take them to the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put the empty plates on the right side of the bar counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wines are here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the glasses go on the shelf here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is also wine on top of the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The orders should go here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wine goes on top of the bar, \N the glasses go over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pleased to meet you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're not going to be working \N as a waitress in {\i1}this{\i0} restaurant, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's wrong with {\i1}this {\i0}restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Anna is going to be our waitress from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna, can I get a carbonara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna, I'd like a bolognese.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna, could you come over here and give me some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, in a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An order of carbonara and bolognese here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the vongole and rigatoni,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the fettuccine too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rosso,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where did you pick up a cutie like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to pick up anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could take you out to somewhere better than this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?  Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hurt my valuable waitress,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow, that cry-baby Rosso is talking like he's got guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the thing, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He started crying when he \N was watching a movie at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An extra order of squid ink risotto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are playing "Summertime."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are playing "Summertime" at the classic movie theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankfurt has so many movie theaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was showing on TV the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I cried so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The movie takes place in a city in Italy called Venice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Venice is a city from medieval times,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is known as a city of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was originally built on a lagoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there are \N waterways running throughout the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to take you there some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been there, Mr. Rosso?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the music in the movie is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that you have
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at least heard the theme song once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go see it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can still get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would run late if you went now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.  Thanks for letting me off work in the afternoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't get many customers at this time anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to ask questions, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of my business what you do on your break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I go to... practice shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I go to Mr. Venkel's shooting range.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you go to Venkel's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, he's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rosso, have you ever fired a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guns?  No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the shakes from just seeing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.  Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how it turned out this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The garlic, the olive oil, and the parsley...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you've probably killed the \N taste of the other stuff you in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:14:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that's not real pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rosso, the bathroom is open now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodni -
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there was a \N movie like this when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rosso...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were always crying while watching movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was young, I didn't have the time for movies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even when I wanted to watch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I ate a lot of good food back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't remember the taste of a single thing I ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even know the taste of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The taste of sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also checked you out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missing, after her parents were \N murdered by unidentified individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want me to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about having you... teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you figure out who I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a law professor at my college,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who had been researching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ristorante Nino homicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Sacco-Milano case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the bomb assassination of Mr. Sabatini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In each of the three murder cases, \N you were summoned as a possible suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though all were committed using different methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, none of the cases were \N prosecuted, due to lack of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the professor had an interesting hypothesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in which you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,undoubtedly a professional hitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An extremely top notch one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many people do you think I have killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a member of the organization before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stealing, extortion... I could do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I was a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could eat good food with the rewards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a big deal;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same routine on that day, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like on all the other days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a café in the middle of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I aimed my gun at this person I didn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who might have been the hundredth person I would kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had ordered coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, he began to put sugar in his coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One spoonful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two spoonfuls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three spoonfuls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four spoonfuls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he put the fifth spoonful of sugar in,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the taste of the coffee I usually \N drank spread through my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person drank the coffee as if it tasted great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I put my down my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that, and I couldn't kill anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you ask me to teach you how to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the six months you were with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I realized I shouldn't force you to get involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Rosso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing people is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget the taste of sugar.
